Some useful swig statements (tags):

- autoescape:
{% autoescape true %}{{ your_var }}{% endautoescape %}

- If
{% if condition %}
	statement1
{% elseif condition2 %}
	statement2
{% else %}
	statement3
{% endif %}

- For
{% for x in obj %}
	statement
{% endfor %}

	Some built-in variables for for-loop:
	-- loop.first: True if the current object is the first in the object/array.
	-- loop.last: True if the current object is the last in the object/array.
